417
00:40:15,334 --> 00:40:16,459
If you can't,

418
00:40:17,584 --> 00:40:19,084
then you must turn back.

419
00:40:20,501 --> 00:40:22,084
I'll wait here for you.

420
00:41:18,376 --> 00:41:20,959
So I've heard

421
00:41:21,126 --> 00:41:21,959
Amitabha

