what can Buddhism teach a king?

492
00:58:59,667 --> 00:59:00,792
What I know is this:

493
00:59:01,084 --> 00:59:03,334
to safeguard the country,
be charitable and upright,

494
00:59:03,917 --> 00:59:05,959
